{"tid":1278248,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"街上跌銀包測全球公民誠實度，邊個國家嘅人最唔老實？","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T00:24:56.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0f4304ec06be6717d7721ac3b89a280fcf2002","tid":1278248,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/27753/街上掉錢包測全球公民誠實度-哪國人最不老實/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F27753%2F%E8%A1%97%E4%B8%8A%E6%8E%89%E9%8C%A2%E5%8C%85%E6%B8%AC%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%E5%BA%A6-%E5%93%AA%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%80%E4%B8%8D%E8%80%81%E5%AF%A6%2F1%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPvcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=ffbbf616\" target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/27753/街上掉錢包測全球公民誠實度-哪國人最不老實/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n大家如果在街上撿到錢包，你會還給失主嗎？美國《科學》期刊日前發布了一項有關全球公民誠實度的大型實驗調查。研究觀察全球40個國家，發現人們傾向歸還「有錢的錢包」多於「沒有錢的錢包」。調查結果顯示瑞士國民誠實度最高，即使錢包內沒有錢，中國國民的歸還率也少於10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20190624134412__merlin_156729945_74696032-f5b2-45f5-9179-265d63dd6874-superJumbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20190624134412__merlin_156729945_74696032-f5b2-45f5-9179-265d63dd6874-superJumbo.jpg&h=5b8ce520&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n美國《科學》(Science) 期刊於上週四發布了一項有關全球公民誠實度(Civic Honesty around the Globe)的大型實驗調查，觀察了全球40個國家，並在355個城市中的公營及私營設施內放置共17,303個「有錢」和「無錢」的錢包，來測試各國國民的誠實度。透明錢包內放有0元或是相等於$13.45美金(約$105港幣)的當地貨幣、3張相同的卡片、鑰匙和一張購物清單。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20190624134403__cohn1HR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20190624134403__cohn1HR.jpg&h=5c056f1e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n調查員在每國公或私營設施附近稱自己在街上撿到錢包，但由於趕時間的關係只好拜託其他途人歸還失主，看看途人會否在100天內聯絡卡片上印有的電郵地址。調查發現不論錢包有錢與否，瑞士國民的整體歸還率都高於80%，其次是挪威跟荷蘭，平均維持70%左右。而中國、摩洛哥、秘魯的誠實度最低，就算錢包內沒有錢，中國國民願意歸還的百分比少於10%，為當中最低<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20190624134409__F1.large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20190624134409__F1.large.jpg&h=8646e34c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"16802a84f4efbc5415471c0b3d888a1f74649a85","tid":1278248,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"研究更在美國、英國、波蘭重新進行實驗，並投入$94.15美金(約$734.37港幣) 於錢包。調查結果顯示錢包歸還率比先前$13.45美金(約$105港幣)的高。證明了當錢包金額越高，人們願意歸還的比率也會相對提升。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/news_photo/w600/20190624134410__F2.large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fnews_photo%2Fw600%2F20190624134410__F2.large.jpg&h=d5c65e22&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2019/06/19/science.aau8712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2Fscience.aau8712&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPvcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=d6055381\" target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2019/06/19/science.aau8712</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voanews.com/usa/honestly-youre-more-likely-return-lost-wallet-cash-inside\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fusa%2Fhonestly-youre-more-likely-return-lost-wallet-cash-inside&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPvcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=1253499b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voanews.com/usa/honestly-youre-more-likely-return-lost-wallet-cash-inside</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/06/20/science/lost-wallet-what-to-do.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F06%2F20%2Fscience%2Flost-wallet-what-to-do.html&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPvcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=845ba60a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/06/20/science/lost-wallet-what-to-do.html</a>"},{"pid":"78161a78d64a994c7c796cd957d7d8af9bee9cb7","tid":1278248,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T23:58:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">就算錢包內沒有錢，中國國民願意歸還的百分比少於10%</span><br />\n<br />\n下，竟然唔勒索返失主？！"},{"pid":"0d2a69f50ea9b4e9fd179bd24285d044c3878017","tid":1278248,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:24:56.000Z","msg":"未睇內文已估支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}